    },
    {
      "time": 91.41,
      "time_str": "01:31.410",
      "text": "It was almost love, it was almost...",
      "translation": "差一点就是爱，差一点"
    },
    {
      "time": 95.72,
      "time_str": "01:35.720",
      "text": "We bleed ourselves in vain",
      "translation": "我们流尽鲜红血液"
    },
    {
      "time": 98.23,
      "time_str": "01:38.230",
      "text": "How tragic is this game?",
      "translation": "这游戏如此悲剧收幕"
    },
    {
      "time": 101.42,
      "time_str": "01:41.420",
      "text": "Turn around, I'm holding on to someone",
      "translation": "拥抱着别人重来一次"
    },
    {
      "time": 104.79,
      "time_str": "01:44.790",
      "text": "But the love is gone",
      "translation": "但爱却已消散"
    },
    {
      "time": 106.99,
      "time_str": "01:46.990",
      "text": "Carrying the load, with wings that feel like stone",
      "translation": "我的羽翼如岩石般沉重"
    },
    {
      "time": 112.63,
      "time_str": "01:52.630",
      "text": "Knowing that we nearly fell so far now",
      "translation": "我们越飘越远"
    },
    {
      "time": 116.54,
      "time_str": "01:56.540",
      "text": "It's hard to tell",
      "translation": "我已看不清你"
    },
    {
      "time": 119.45,
      "time_str": "01:59.450",
      "text": "Yeah we came so close, it was almost love",
      "translation": "曾经如此紧密，差一点就是爱"
    },
